    public class OptionsMenuDialog
extends javax.swing.JDialog
    This class implements the graphic view to show as option menu dialog.

    This class contains all the graphic elements needed to show when the option menu is called. The different elements that contains are all related with the configuration options of the application therefore all the JLabel, JPanel, JComboBox and JCheckBox are used to configure the language, window resolution, look and feel and color blindness mode options.
